n CPUT<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/cape-peninsula-university-of-technology-cput-online-application\/#Is_National_Benchmark_Test_NBT_required_for_CPUT_admission_2024\" title=\"Is National Benchmark Test (NBT) required for CPUT admission 2024?\">Is National Benchmark Test (NBT) required for CPUT admission 2024?<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<p><strong>Table of Contents<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80720789\">About the Cape Peninsula University of Technology (CPUT) Online Application 2024<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80720790\"><strong>How to Apply for CPUT Application 2024<\/strong><\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80720791\">Documents Required for CPUT Online Application 2024<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80720792\">CPUT Application Fees 2024<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80720793\">Application Deadline:<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80720794\">Applying for Financial Assistance in CPUT<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80720795\">Is National Benchmark Test (NBT) required for CPUT admission 2024?<\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"about-the-cape-peninsula-university-of-technology-cput-online-application-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"About_the_Cape_Peninsula_University_of_Technology_CPUT_Online_Application_2024\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80720789\"><\/a>About the Cape Peninsula University of Technology (CPUT) Online Application 2024<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>This is to inform all and sundry that the management of the Cape Peninsula University of Technology(CPUT) is inviting applications from interested and suitably qualified students (Indigenes and International) for admission into undergraduate and postgraduate programmes for the 2024 academic year.<\/p>\n<p>Before you apply, see the know the actual programs (Courses) available for the 2024 admission.<\/p>\n<p><a name=\"_Toc80720790\"><\/a><strong>How to Apply for CPUT Application 2024<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Visit <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cput.ac.za\/study\/apply\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">here<\/a><\/li>\n<li>select undergraduate\/postgraduate\/semester study abroad<\/li>\n<li>Create an Account with your valid email on the portal.<\/li>\n<li>Fill all necessary forms.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"documents-required-for-cput-admission-application-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Documents_Required_for_CPUT_Admission_Application_2024\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80720791\"><\/a>Documents Required for CPUT Admission Application 2024<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Valid Email<\/li>\n<li>South African Identity Number<\/li>\n<li>Passport Number (International Students)<\/li>\n<li>Final School results<\/li>\n<li>Valid Passport or Identity Document or Birth Certificate<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"cput-application-fees-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"CPUT_Application_Fees_2024\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80720792\"><\/a>CPUT Application Fees 2024<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Pay a non-refundable application fee of R100 for South African citizens<\/li>\n<li>Pay a non-refundable application fee for foreign citizens of R700<\/li>\n<li>Payments to be made before closing dates<\/li>\n<li>Ensure to use your Person Number or T Number as a reference<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"application-deadline\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Application_Deadline\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80720793\"><\/a>Application Deadline:<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>30\u00a0September 2024<\/strong><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"applying-for-financial-assistance-in-cput\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Applying_for_Financial_Assistance_in_CPUT\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80720794\"><\/a>Applying for Financial Assistance in CPUT<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Interested applicants can apply for financial assistance (Scholarship) through the NSFAS application portal <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cput.ac.za\/study\/funding\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https:\/\/www.cput.ac.za\/study\/funding<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.cput.ac.za\/study\/apply\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Click here to Apply<\/a><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"is-national-benchmark-test-nbt-required-for-cput-admission-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Is_National_Benchmark_Test_NBT_required_for_CPUT_admission_2024\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80720795\"><\/a>Is National Benchmark Test (NBT) required for CPUT admission 2024?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>Yes.<\/strong><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"CPUT Online Application 2024 for Admission into Cape Peninsula University of Technology, CPUT Application fees, Programs (Courses), Application&hellip;\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1138,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[12],"tags":[65],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1137"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1137"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1137\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1137"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1137"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2